{"tid":1699002,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[cpu換液金] 金屬觸點及電阻應該用邊隻膠水密封？","createTime":"2019-11-08T01:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T12:53:47.000Z","uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3e9e41d77afc53e3ce7960a068a4532d9a0c74e7","tid":1699002,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T01:36:15.000Z","msg":"小弟想幫部notebook cpu換液金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nnotebook cpu如下圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5JsDvM3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5JsDvM3.jpg&h=179415f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n液金雖然導熱散熱強 但導電<br />\n所以想搵隻3M膠水將die附近電阻同金屬點密封<br />\n紅色部份：金屬觸電  黃色部份：電阻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7E55VeJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7E55VeJ.jpg&h=f413329f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問用3M邊隻膠水先正確？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5398028150804146adbe5ea72fa62547fa0cceda","tid":1699002,"uid":81308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T02:35:10.000Z","msg":"指甲油"},{"pid":"6dd0408a32013146602b232ddf2255ab4103c5b9","tid":1699002,"uid":25170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T04:10:30.000Z","msg":"LM 學嘢"},{"pid":"262faf125d816dd0b71c0e13edaa440a3f524962","tid":1699002,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dd0408a32013146602b232ddf2255ab4103c5b9","tid":1699002,"uid":25170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T04:10:30.000Z","msg":"LM 學嘢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T04:58:57.000Z","msg":"準備過幾日去買幾種矽膠水（矽氧樹脂）<br />\n同環氧樹脂做測試"},{"pid":"17a41bf166c71031ccbf24dc12d821b82cfad71c","tid":1699002,"uid":16240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:02:46.000Z","msg":"上網見人用electrical tape/ 指甲油<br />\n我上次開蓋就用指甲油 so far so good"},{"pid":"d94a0391f4cf81bb209acf5deddb27736a977847","tid":1699